The 4!stars are for the employees and the products. This Starbucks is consistent in the quality and speed of service. However, the bathrooms are absolutely disgusting every time. (Not the employees fault) There is no ventilation system in the bathroom and it smells like a port-a-pot every time. Then, to wash your hands the sink has almost no pressure in giving water. It’s a trickle. I feel gross after using this restroom. It’s not expensive to put in a fan system or to update the faucet on the sink. Thank you for everything else though, I enjoy the coffee and pastries.
